    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with ASME V&V 40 Table 3 requirements for MRL 2. Experimental validation demonstrates CFD predictions of hemolysis index are within acceptable error bounds across all five operating points. The simulation evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory claim that the device hemolysis does not exceed the predicate device under worst-case operating conditions.",
